Question: Many universities require that freshman live on campus dorm during the first year of college. In your opinion, is this a good or a bad thing? Explain your opinion on this issue.
Answer:
I think is is good to require freshman live on campus dorm during the first year of college. Freshman is new to the area and may not know the area very well, they might get lost, and they have so many things to get used to and learn that they better stay on campus to save time. Besides they will get to know their classmates better by living close to each other.